# Business Rule Traceability

> Source of truth: `SU26SE049_BusinessRules_v1_0.docx`. Module map in `CLAUDE.md §5`.

## Mandatory: BR ID in XML doc on every business handler

```csharp
/// <summary>
/// Verify a submitted pollution report.
/// </summary>
/// <remarks>
/// Implements: BR-REP-020 (state machine), BR-OFF-002 (verify SLA 24h),
/// BR-OFF-004 (segregation of duties), BR-ADM-010 (audit log).
/// </remarks>
public sealed class VerifyReportCommandHandler : IRequestHandler<VerifyReportCommand, Result>
```

## Mandatory: BR ID in test names

Pattern: `{Method}_{Scenario}_{ExpectedResult}_{BR_ID}`

```csharp
[Fact]
public async Task SubmitReport_NoPhoto_ReturnsValidationError_BR_REP_001() { ... }

[Fact]
public async Task Verify_FromSubmitted_ChangesStatus_BR_REP_020() { ... }
```

**Every BR ID listed in a handler MUST have at least 1 test.**

## Mandatory: BR ID in commit messages

Conventional Commits + BR IDs:

```
feat(reports): submit report endpoint (BR-REP-001..013, BR-REP-030)
fix(auth): correct lockout window calculation (BR-AUTH-011)
```

## Module → folder map

| Prefix       | Folder                                       |
|--------------|----------------------------------------------|
| `BR-AUTH-*`  | `Application/Features/Auth/*`                |
| `BR-REP-*`   | `Application/Features/Reports/*`             |
| `BR-MAP-*`   | `Application/Features/Map/*`                 |
| `BR-OFF-*`   | `Application/Features/Officer/*`             |
| `BR-CLN-*`   | `Application/Features/Cleanup/*`             |
| `BR-NTF-*`   | `Application/Features/Notifications/*`       |
| `BR-CMT-*`   | `Application/Features/Comments/*`            |
| `BR-GAM-*`   | `Application/Features/Gamification/*`        |
| `BR-AI-*`    | `Infrastructure/Ai/*`                        |
| `BR-ADM-*`   | `Application/Features/Admin/*`               |
| `BR-DAT-*`   | infrastructure-level (cross-cutting)         |
| `BR-SYS-*`   | infrastructure-level (hosting/non-functional)|

## When BR is unclear

**STOP** and ask the user: "BR-XXX-yyy chưa rõ điểm Z, anh/chị xác nhận giúp?" — never invent rules.
